	   <tr><td colspan=2>Everyone keeps going on about how wonderful the haste is but in my opingion, that is NOT the most valuable quality of this belt, there are many items with comperable haste by the time you could aquire this belt, the AC (obviously) is quite nice too but to me, the 7 to all saves is what puts it over the top.&nbsp;&nbsp;For high-end zones such as ToV, VP, etc. you are dealing with alot of AoE mobs where saves are really important.  Not to downplay the emmense value of AC but in such situations, the AC only benefits the MT most of the time while EVERYONE there needs to be concerned with the AoE thus saves become the overwhelmingly most valuable stat; it doesn't matter what kind of damage you are capable of dealing if you are killed in about 30secs cause every AoE hit you for its max damage... Between the excelent AC, high haste percentage, and the saves, this belt is among the most well rounded and overall valueable belts around, i cannot think of better offhand though there may well be better; then agian its possible that this is the best, that title has to be bestowed upon one belt or another hehe.<br>&nbsp;<br>Ok, I'll shut up now.<br><br>Baron Slein Jinn &lt;Dawn of Redemption&gt;<br>Grave Lord on everyone's least favorite server, E'ci<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=325772" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=325772</a></td></tr>
