	   <tr><td colspan=2>Your damage will increase by a certain amount determined by your haste.&nbsp;&nbsp;You can calculate haste two different ways.  Percent increase in Dmg OR percent decrease in Dly.  They are seperate and calculated differently.   You WILL attack more often, thus, doing +x% dmg over certain amount of time.  People say FBSS is 21% haste...they are right.  People say FBSS is 16% haste...they are correct.  First is percent dmg increase...second is percent dly decrease.<br><br>That explain better?<br><br>Ahnoksuna<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
